embeds.title: New Cards
embeds.description: Prepare to expand your deck and engage in thrilling battles, as we introduce the latest star to join our galaxy:**Director Krennic**! With his ambition and cunning, Krennic is here to lead your forces to victory.

fields.name: <:Krennic:1162771579852304394> Director Krennic
fields.value: Director Orson Krennic is the mastermind behind the construction of the Death Star, and he's not to be underestimated. His strategic genius and drive to achieve his goals make him a formidable adversary and a powerful ally. Will you harness the power of the Death Star under his command, or will you challenge his ambitions with your own? The choice is yours!
